Trajecto: Real-time 3D Trajectory Reconstruction System


Copyright 2025-2026 Eunkyum Kim

I. Principal Architectures & Methodologies
This project incorporates original architectures and methodologies developed by Eunkyum Kim, representing a vertical integration of hardware control, state estimation, and deep learning. Key technical pillars include:

Hybrid ESKF-Stateful TCN: A closed-loop control architecture integrating Error-State Kalman Filters with Temporal Convolutional Networks .

Non-linear Reverse Engineering of Hovering: A methodology for reconstructing physical depth from normalized 2D digitizer signals using exponential modeling .

O(1) Stateful Inference: Optimized real-time inference using ring buffers for resource-constrained edge devices .


